WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.669
Good morning, family. I have a very strong

00:00:02.679 --> 00:00:06.150
prophetic warning to give right now.

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:07.990
Last night I was praying, and in my

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.830
prayer time, the Lord opened my eyes

00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:13.190
to the spirit realm. He said, "Brandon,

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.630
the last visions have come and

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:19.550
they've gone."What the Lord showed me

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:21.990
about New Orleans and Las Vegas

00:00:21.990 --> 00:00:22.000
has

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.630
happened. So now He said, "I'm going to

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:26.589
show you the next wave of things that you

00:00:26.589 --> 00:00:26.599
are

00:00:26.599 --> 00:00:28.790
to warn the body for what

00:00:28.790 --> 00:00:28.800
is coming."It

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:32.030
all started

00:00:32.030 --> 00:00:32.040
while

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:33.549
I was just worshipping and praying

00:00:33.559 --> 00:00:35.190
like I normally do, and all of

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:36.950
a sudden, it was as if a vision was being put out in front of me. I

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:38.869
told my wife, "Get the phone,

00:00:38.869 --> 00:00:38.879
you've

00:00:38.879 --> 00:00:40.910
got to record

00:00:42.630 --> 00:00:42.640
it."I

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:48.869
saw massive farming

00:00:48.879 --> 00:00:51.950
equipment on

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.510
the East Coast,

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:56.670
and there were

00:00:56.680 --> 00:00:59.310
silos. The Lord said, "I want

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.709
you to focus on

00:01:01.709 --> 00:01:01.719
fertilizer."All

00:01:01.719 --> 00:01:04.509
of a sudden,

00:01:04.519 --> 00:01:06.670
everything was coming at me very

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:11.109
fast. I could see these men buying

00:01:11.119 --> 00:01:14.749
lots of fertilizer since this summer

00:01:14.759 --> 00:01:17.510
over the course of quite a while.

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:23.950
I have to describe what I saw: I

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:27.910
saw

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:31.069
trees with leaves,

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:33.670
summer grass growing—it was hot

00:01:33.670 --> 00:01:33.680
outside—and

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:37.630
I saw these men collecting

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:40.350
fertilizer through different

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:42.710
places so that they would not be

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:45.670
detected,

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:49.469
buying in bulk

00:01:49.479 --> 00:01:51.630
without drawing

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:54.109
suspicion.

00:01:54.119 --> 00:01:56.029
These men were storing this

00:01:56.039 --> 00:02:01.190
fertilizer.

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.469
I

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:04.350
saw

00:02:04.360 --> 00:02:07.190
massive dump

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:11.470
trucks with separation in the back

00:02:11.480 --> 00:02:15.390
containing

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:16.710
50-gallon

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:19.790
drums filled with different

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:22.949
chemicals to make what happened in

00:02:22.959 --> 00:02:25.750
Oklahoma City back in the

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:29.589
'90s. This

00:02:29.589 --> 00:02:29.599
was

00:02:29.599 --> 00:02:32.150
not black

00:02:32.160 --> 00:02:35.750
powder, but this fertilizer stuff

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:39.149
in a big

00:02:39.149 --> 00:02:39.159
diesel

00:02:39.159 --> 00:02:43.869
dump truck that

00:02:43.869 --> 00:02:43.879
looked

00:02:43.879 --> 00:02:45.589
like a

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:53.990
construction

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:57.149
vehicle.

00:02:57.159 --> 00:03:01.990
They put all this in so that it

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:05.470
would cause a major catastrophic

00:03:05.480 --> 00:03:10.470
event. They made the front of it

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:15.309
bulletproof

00:03:15.319 --> 00:03:18.750
with

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:21.789
very strong armor so you could not shoot it

00:03:21.789 --> 00:03:21.799
to stop it. This armor was

00:03:21.799 --> 00:03:26.470
underneath, so

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:28.589
it wasn't easily seen.

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:39.949
I saw these men with

00:03:39.949 --> 00:03:39.959
vests

00:03:39.959 --> 00:03:44.309
on in the front cab of the

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:48.670
truck, and they had explosives on

00:03:48.680 --> 00:03:51.949
these vests. There were two men in the

00:03:51.959 --> 00:03:55.350
truck, and they

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:58.069
used it to go through police

00:03:58.079 --> 00:04:01.429
and military barricades

00:04:01.429 --> 00:04:01.439
in

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:04.270
Washington,

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:07.350
D.C. When they tried

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:09.069
to stop them

00:04:09.079 --> 00:04:11.509
at a checkpoint, they

00:04:11.519 --> 00:04:13.309
pushed through the barricade because

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:14.949
the truck was very

00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:17.870
strong. Then they

00:04:17.870 --> 00:04:17.880
were

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:19.990
surrounded, they ignited

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:23.430
their vests, and they took out

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:26.909
everybody. When this happened, there was

00:04:26.919 --> 00:04:29.950
a massive crater in the

00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:31.990
ground and all the buildings were

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.590
completely wiped out. They tried to

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.430
get as close as they could to the

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:38.189
Capitol

00:04:38.199 --> 00:04:40.150
and

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:44.230
major landmarks of Washington,

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:48.070
D.C. The Lord spoke

00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:50.629
to me about

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:52.189
lone

00:04:52.199 --> 00:04:57.350
wolves in America. They were

00:04:57.360 --> 00:05:00.550
sympathetic

00:05:03.590 --> 00:05:03.600
to

00:05:06.479 --> 00:05:08.749
terrorism, acting

00:05:08.749 --> 00:05:08.759
alone.

00:05:08.759 --> 00:05:10.070
They

00:05:10.070 --> 00:05:10.080
are

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:11.870
part of an organization, but they

00:05:11.870 --> 00:05:11.880
are

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:14.629
not part of a big group. I saw

00:05:14.639 --> 00:05:16.870
different

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:19.870
individuals

00:05:19.880 --> 00:05:22.070
throughout towns acting alone.

00:05:26.639 --> 00:05:28.870
There were lots of them, and

00:05:28.880 --> 00:05:30.510
they weren't necessarily illegal immigrants from

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:33.670
across the border;

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:36.230
they were people

00:05:36.230 --> 00:05:36.240
who

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:38.150
already lived here.

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:44.270
The Lord showed me

00:05:44.280 --> 00:05:48.950
white cargo vans

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:50.990
with no windows on the side that would

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:54.749
carry

00:05:54.759 --> 00:05:57.469
50-gallon

00:05:57.479 --> 00:06:01.070
drums

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:10.070
of fertilizer.

00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:12.270
They were parking them in New

00:06:12.280 --> 00:06:14.510
York City in parking garages and

00:06:14.520 --> 00:06:16.550
close to buildings so they did not look

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:21.029
suspicious. I saw them trying to

00:06:21.039 --> 00:06:25.390
get as close as they could to Trump

00:06:25.400 --> 00:06:29.950
Towers, and they had a plan to take

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:34.350
out Trump Towers and golf courses throughout

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:36.390
America.

00:06:40.520 --> 00:06:43.390
The Lord spoke to me and said,

00:06:43.400 --> 00:06:46.790
"This is bigger than

00:06:46.790 --> 00:06:46.800
terrorists."I

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:50.189
saw it was in retaliation for Qasem

00:06:50.189 --> 00:06:50.199
Soleimani,

00:06:50.199 --> 00:06:52.629
the man that was taken

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:56.189
out in Iraq. I saw that man's face, and

00:06:56.199 --> 00:07:00.629
they said, "We have not forgotten his

00:07:00.629 --> 00:07:00.639
assassination."They

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:03.430
were coming

00:07:03.440 --> 00:07:07.270
against America, especially Trump,

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:09.150
in

00:07:09.160 --> 00:07:12.029
retaliation for what happened

00:07:12.039 --> 00:07:16.029
in Iran. I saw this was a

00:07:16.039 --> 00:07:19.430
government operation with a thousand

00:07:19.440 --> 00:07:25.670
men coming through

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:29.510
underground drug

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:30.790
trafficking

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:36.270
tunnels. This is

00:07:36.270 --> 00:07:36.280
a multi-hundred-million-dollar

00:07:36.280 --> 00:07:39.270
operation that

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:40.950
has been going on

00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:42.390
for

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:44.230
the last four years,

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:47.230
gathering supplies, and they are

00:07:47.240 --> 00:07:52.309
here. I saw darkness in ten major cities,

00:07:52.309 --> 00:07:52.319
with

00:07:55.909 --> 00:07:55.919
groups

00:07:58.350 --> 00:07:58.360
of

00:07:58.360 --> 00:08:00.110
a

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:04.830
hundred

00:08:04.840 --> 00:08:09.550
people per

00:08:09.550 --> 00:08:09.560
attack

00:08:09.560 --> 00:08:12.390
coming out of

00:08:12.400 --> 00:08:15.270
the ground like ants. The Lord said, "This

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:18.390
is not terrorists per se; this is an act

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:21.749
of war."This is

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:24.589
a government of another country coming

00:08:24.599 --> 00:08:27.909
against America, making it look like

00:08:27.909 --> 00:08:27.919
terrorism.

00:08:27.919 --> 00:08:31.149
You will see

00:08:31.159 --> 00:08:36.110
a great shaking still to come

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:38.750
because of past administrations not

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:42.990
securing the

00:08:44.949 --> 00:08:44.959
borders.

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:50.389
I warn you to

00:08:50.389 --> 00:08:50.399
pray—not

00:08:50.399 --> 00:08:52.750
a call to fear, but a call to

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:56.310
prayer. I saw plans and plots

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:59.990
from these men to try to disrupt

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:01.509
the

00:09:01.519 --> 00:09:05.150
inauguration. After the election,

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:09.269
I heard the word

00:09:09.279 --> 00:09:11.870
"strike"five

00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:14.910
times.

00:09:14.920 --> 00:09:17.110
These

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:19.990
were

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:25.389
major events

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:28.630
trying to bring fear upon

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:30.870
the American people.

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:42.509
We must pray for what

00:09:42.519 --> 00:09:45.670
is dear to Trump, specifically his

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:48.630
children. This is about retaliation,

00:09:51.949 --> 00:09:51.959
with

00:09:55.040 --> 00:09:58.550
funding

00:09:58.550 --> 00:09:58.560
hidden

00:09:58.560 --> 00:10:00.430
through crypto

00:10:00.430 --> 00:10:00.440
and

00:10:00.440 --> 00:10:02.630
communication

00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:05.350
through untraceable sources.

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:07.550
It

00:10:07.560 --> 00:10:11.350
is

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:13.350
about Syria and things

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:16.389
happening as America lines up

00:10:16.399 --> 00:10:18.509
with Israel.

00:10:22.509 --> 00:10:22.519
We

00:10:25.560 --> 00:10:27.509
pray protection over your families,

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:33.670
our President,

00:10:33.670 --> 00:10:33.680
and

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:36.670
the capital of America.

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:41.030
This was very

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.829
dark;

00:10:43.839 --> 00:10:45.710
these people obviously do not value

00:10:45.720 --> 00:10:48.870
their own

00:10:48.880 --> 00:10:50.750
lives.

00:10:50.760 --> 00:10:52.110
When they

00:10:52.110 --> 00:10:52.120
ignited

00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:54.870
their vests, it was a

00:10:54.880 --> 00:10:57.509
massive explosion, bigger than

00:10:57.519 --> 00:11:00.949
Oklahoma City.

00:11:00.959 --> 00:11:03.310
It was

00:11:03.320 --> 00:11:05.670
fertilizer, and I am

00:11:05.670 --> 00:11:05.680
trying

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:06.990
to

00:11:06.990 --> 00:11:07.000
communicate

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:09.829
what I

00:11:09.839 --> 00:11:12.150
see in

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:14.629
the spirit.

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:29.750
These vans were

00:11:29.750 --> 00:11:29.760
targeted at

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:33.150
Trump hotels

00:11:33.150 --> 00:11:33.160
and

00:11:33.160 --> 00:11:35.629
locations.

00:11:35.639 --> 00:11:38.990
It

00:11:39.000 --> 00:11:41.990
is

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:44.470
a network of

00:11:46.519 --> 00:11:48.350
people who

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:49.990
want to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:55.949
It was also about Europe,

00:11:57.720 --> 00:12:00.470
including

00:12:02.399 --> 00:12:07.829
France and

00:12:07.839 --> 00:12:11.470
England.

00:12:11.470 --> 00:12:11.480
I

00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:16.069
am

00:12:16.079 --> 00:12:18.670
not

00:12:18.680 --> 00:12:21.550
here to stir up fear, but the

00:12:21.560 --> 00:12:24.030
last visions I saw came to pass, and

00:12:24.040 --> 00:12:25.310
now the Lord is

00:12:25.310 --> 00:12:25.320
giving

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:28.269
more.

00:12:47.519 --> 00:12:49.230
I

00:12:49.240 --> 00:12:51.629
believe we lessened what happened in New Orleans by

00:12:51.639 --> 00:12:54.069
prayer. In

00:12:56.120 --> 00:12:59.670
Las Vegas,

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:01.470
God used a

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:03.470
bulletproof Cybertruck to shoot the blast

00:13:03.480 --> 00:13:05.150
straight up, so the glass at the Trump building did not even break.

00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:10.150
Even

00:13:10.160 --> 00:13:12.430
the tires were not

00:13:12.440 --> 00:13:14.430
popped.

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:18.350
While

00:13:18.360 --> 00:13:19.949
people lost their lives in New Orleans,

00:13:19.949 --> 00:13:19.959
where

00:13:19.959 --> 00:13:21.949
there

00:13:21.949 --> 00:13:21.959
is

00:13:21.959 --> 00:13:24.430
a

00:13:24.440 --> 00:13:26.629
strong presence of witchcraft on

00:13:26.639 --> 00:13:28.790
Bourbon Street,

00:13:38.069 --> 00:13:38.079
we

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:47.550
can

00:13:49.310 --> 00:13:49.320
stop

00:13:51.680 --> 00:13:54.829
these events

00:13:54.839 --> 00:13:57.590
through

00:13:57.600 --> 00:14:01.470
prayer.

00:14:01.480 --> 00:14:04.910
My job is to raise up a

00:14:04.910 --> 00:14:04.920
million-person

00:14:04.920 --> 00:14:07.910
prayer army

00:14:07.920 --> 00:14:09.629
to

00:14:09.639 --> 00:14:12.670
change events

00:14:12.680 --> 00:14:16.150
in politics and

00:14:16.150 --> 00:14:16.160
the

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:19.110
financial realm.

00:14:26.920 --> 00:14:29.350
It

00:14:38.600 --> 00:14:41.790
is

00:14:48.279 --> 00:14:50.749
time to

00:14:50.759 --> 00:14:52.910
rise and shine, for the light has come.

00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:03.389
You have the ability to

00:15:03.399 --> 00:15:05.470
tread on serpents and scorpions, and

00:15:05.480 --> 00:15:07.749
nothing shall by any means hurt you. He

00:15:07.759 --> 00:15:10.069
gave His angels

00:15:10.069 --> 00:15:10.079
charge

00:15:10.079 --> 00:15:12.150
to bear us up in their hands lest we

00:15:12.160 --> 00:15:14.790
dash our foot against a stone. It

00:15:14.790 --> 00:15:14.800
is

00:15:14.800 --> 00:15:18.749
time for the body of Christ

00:15:21.279 --> 00:15:23.910
to take

00:15:23.920 --> 00:15:26.030
our authority.

00:15:30.680 --> 00:15:32.389
I believe we will see

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:36.749
great changes.

00:15:36.749 --> 00:15:36.759
New

00:15:36.759 --> 00:15:40.430
Orleans

00:15:40.430 --> 00:15:40.440
was

00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:42.710
tragic, but

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:45.110
it could have been worse.

00:15:52.839 --> 00:15:53.990
Pipe bombs did

00:15:53.990 --> 00:15:54.000
not

00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:56.829
go off

00:15:56.829 --> 00:15:56.839
and

00:15:56.839 --> 00:15:58.990
churches were not affected.

00:16:13.199 --> 00:16:15.710
This will be a year

00:16:15.720 --> 00:16:19.309
of great acceleration and

00:16:19.309 --> 00:16:19.319
an

00:16:19.319 --> 00:16:21.230
outpouring of

00:16:21.230 --> 00:16:21.240
the

00:16:21.240 --> 00:16:23.470
Spirit. I talked to

00:16:23.470 --> 00:16:23.480
an elderly Jewish

00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:26.870
man

00:16:32.959 --> 00:16:35.150
about

00:16:35.160 --> 00:16:38.069
the

00:16:38.079 --> 00:16:40.230
tradition of the groom giving

00:16:40.230 --> 00:16:40.240
presents

00:16:40.240 --> 00:16:42.230
to

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:44.949
the

00:16:44.959 --> 00:16:47.710
bride.

00:16:47.720 --> 00:16:50.030
He said that

00:16:50.030 --> 00:16:50.040
was an

00:16:50.040 --> 00:16:51.790
old tradition, and that

00:16:51.800 --> 00:16:53.309
is

00:16:53.319 --> 00:16:56.870
what

00:16:56.880 --> 00:16:58.590
Jesus would go by.

00:17:08.600 --> 00:17:10.710
God

00:17:10.710 --> 00:17:10.720
is

00:17:10.720 --> 00:17:13.350
giving His remnant gifts, and

00:17:15.679 --> 00:17:19.630
huge financial blessings

00:17:19.640 --> 00:17:22.710
are coming to the church.

00:18:04.840 --> 00:18:07.789
In 2025, believe

